Objective: Design a Python-based program "EcoDispose", that guides users
on recycling and disposing of electronic equipment according to local council
guidelines and in compliance with WEEE regulations.


Overview: Green Tech Solutions is seeking to develop a user-friendly Python program that assists
individuals and businesses in responsibly recycling or disposing of electronic equipment. The
program should be designed as an interactive tool that asks users a series of questions about the
electronic equipment they wish to recycle or dispose of. Based on the users' responses, the program
will provide tailored guidance on the appropriate disposal or recycling methods in accordance with the
Waste Electrical and Electronic Equipment (WEEE) Directive and local council regulations.


